                                            Bumblebee

                                            LEGO® Icons
                                            Price$89.99

                                            Available now

                                            Limit 5

                                            Limit

                                            We restrict the limit a household can buy in order to be fair to all of our fans. If you’ve already reached that limit through previous orders your entire order may be cancelled.

                                            Building Instructions

                                            Autobots, roll out!

                                            Known as B-127 on his home planet Cybertron, Bumblebee is often considered the "little brother" of the heroic Autobots. He may be small, but his courage and determination are immeasurable. Designed with Transformers fans in mind, this detailed interpretation of the iconic 1980s Autobot converts from robot to vehicle mode – without rebuilding!

                                            More than meets the eye

                                            Articulated joints for total posability

                                            Features an ion blaster and a jetpack

                                            Display plaque lists power statistics

                                            Show of force

                                            Create the ultimate Transformers display with Optimus Prime (10302).
